<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AttendEase | Event Attendee Management</title>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
            font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
        }

        body{
            background:#f8fafc;
            color:#333;
        }

        header{
            background:#2563eb;
            color:#fff;
            padding:20px 8%;
            display:flex;
            justify-content:space-between;
            align-items:center;
        }

        .logo{
            font-size:28px;
            font-weight:700;
        }

        nav a{
            color:#fff;
            text-decoration:none;
            margin-left:25px;
            font-weight:500;
        }

        .hero{
            display:flex;
            justify-content:space-between;
            align-items:center;
            padding:80px 8%;
            flex-wrap:wrap;
        }

        .hero-text{
            max-width:550px;
        }

        .hero-text h1{
            font-size:50px;
            color:#1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom:20px;
        }

        .hero-text p{
            font-size:18px;
            color:#555;
            line-height:1.8;
            margin-bottom:30px;
        }

        .btn{
            display:inline-block;
            padding:14px 28px;
            background:#2563eb;
            color:white;
            text-decoration:none;
            border-radius:8px;
            transition:.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover{
            background:#1d4ed8;
        }

        .hero img{
            width:450px;
            max-width:100%;
        }

        section{
            padding:70px 8%;
        }

        h2{
            text-align:center;
            margin-bottom:40px;
            color:#1e3a8a;
            font-size:36px;
        }

        .cards{
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
            gap:25px;
        }

        .card{
            background:white;
            padding:30px;
            border-radius:12px;
            box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
            transition:.3s;
        }

        .card:hover{
            transform:translateY(-8px);
        }

        .card h3{
            margin-bottom:15px;
            color:#2563eb;
        }

        footer{
            background:#1e293b;
            color:white;
            text-align:center;
            padding:25px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>

<div class="logo">
AttendEase
</div>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Features</a>
<a href="#">Events</a>
<a href="#">Dashboard</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-text">

<h1>Manage Events with Ease</h1>

<p>
AttendEase is an event attendee management platform that helps organizers create events,
register attendees, manage participant information, and monitor attendance through a simple,
modern dashboard.
</p>

<a href="#" class="btn">Get Started</a>

</div>

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511578314322-379afb476865?w=900" alt="Event">

</section>

<section>

<h2>Key Features</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>🔐 Secure Login</h3>
<p>User authentication with secure access control.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>📅 Event Management</h3>
<p>Create, edit and manage events from a single dashboard.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>👥 Attendee Registration</h3>
<p>Register attendees and maintain participant records.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>📊 Dashboard</h3>
<p>View attendee statistics and event summaries.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🔎 Search</h3>
<p>Quickly search attendees by name or email.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>📱 Responsive</h3>
<p>Works smoothly on desktop, tablet and mobile devices.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section>

<h2>Why AttendEase?</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>Easy to Use</h3>
<p>Simple interface designed for event organizers.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Fast Registration</h3>
<p>Register participants in just a few clicks.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Modern Design</h3>
<p>Clean UI built for better productivity.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 AttendEase | Event Attendee Management System</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
